{"name": "odoo14-addon-sale-automatic-workflow", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-sale-automatic-workflow", "version": "14.0.1.4.0", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo", "openupgradelib"], "summary": "Sale Automatic Workflow", "upload_time": 1697625033}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fsale--workflow-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/sale-workflow\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/14.0/sale_automatic_workflow\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/sale-workflow-14-0/sale-workflow-14-0-sale_automatic_workflow\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/sale-workflow&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Sale Automatic Workflow\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:52b2f19ce8b29634e82b92705aad6586a9533730eab2f35786099f71d006741d\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nCreate workflows with more or less automatization and apply it on sales\norders.\n\nA workflow can:\n\n- Apply default values:\n\n  - Packing Policy (partial, complete)\n  - Shipping Policy (prepaid, manual, postpaid, picking)\n  - Invoice On (ordered quantities, shipped quantities)\n  - Set the invoice's date to the sale order's date\n  - Set a sales team\n\n- Apply automatic actions:\n\n  - Validate the order (only if paid, always, never)\n  - Send order confirmation mail (only when order confirmed)\n  - Create an invoice\n  - Validate the invoice\n  - Confirm the picking\n\nThis module is used by Magentoerpconnect and Prestashoperpconnect.\nIt is well suited for other E-Commerce connectors as well.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues/new?body=module:%20sale_automatic_workflow%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Akretion\n- Camptocamp\n- Sodexis\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Guewen Baconnier\n- Beau Sebastien\n- Leonardo Pistone\n- St\u00e9phane Bidoul\n- Damien Crier\n- Alexandre Fayolle\n- Sodexis\n- Dave Lasley \\<<mailto:dave@laslabs.com>>\n- Akim Juillerat \\<<mailto:akim.juillerat@camptocamp.com>>\n- Thomas Fossoul \\<<mailto:thomas@niboo.com>>\n- Phuc Tran Thanh \\<<mailto:phuc@trobz.com>>\n\n### Other credits\n\nThe development of this module has been financially supported by:\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/sale-workflow](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/14.0/sale_automatic_workflow) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models.account_move", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models..account_move", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models.automatic_workflow_job", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models..automatic_workflow_job", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models.sale_order", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models..sale_order", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models.sale_workflow_process", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models..sale_workflow_process", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models.stock_move", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models..stock_move", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models.stock_picking", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models..stock_picking", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_automatic_workflow.models.account_move", "documentation": ["Copyright 2011 Akretion S\u00e9bastien BEAU <sebastien.beau@akretion.com>", "Copyright 2013 Camptocamp SA (author: Guewen Baconnier